  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Type 1 diabetic patients, 18-60 years of age

          -  Diabetic for &gt;2 years

          -  Treated with CSII for &gt;=6 months

          -  HbA1c &lt;8.5%

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Treatment with daily insulin injections

          -  Inability to handle pump therapy

          -  Untreated retinopathy
      </textblock>
